Title: Multi-leg integrable ladder models
Authors: D. Arnaudon, A. Sedrakyan, T. Sedrakyan
Comments: 20 pages; Latex2e with epic,eepic macros
Report-no: LAPTH-944/02
Subj-class: High Energy Physics - Theory; Quantum Algebra
\\
  We construct integrable spin chains with inhomogeneous periodic disposition
of the anisotropy parameter. The periodicity holds for both auxiliary (space)
and quantum (time) directions. The integrability of the model is based on a set
of coupled Yang-Baxter equations. This construction yields P-leg integrable
ladder Hamiltonians. We analyse the corresponding quantum group symmetry.
